OL,6,FHer accusation against bar owner
OL,7,FPatrick Lumumba appeared in statements
OL,8,Ftyped by police that she signed, but
OL,9,Fthese were ruled inadmissible when her
OL,10,Fprevious slander conviction was thrown
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FInstead, the court will now look at a
OL,14,Ffour-page handwritten note written the
OL,15,Fafternoon after she was questioned by
OL,16,Fpolice in which she recanted the
OL,17,Faccusation.
