OL,3,CItaly opens new slander trial against
OL,4,CAmanda Knox
OL,6,FCourt recessed after nearly four hours
OL,7,Fof arguments and will reconvene June 5
OL,8,Ffor rebuttals and a decision. The case
OL,9,Fis being heard by two professional
OL,10,Fjudges and eight civilian jurors.
OL,12,FDespite Knox's attempts at walking
OL,13,Fback the accusation, Mr Lumumba was
OL,14,Fpicked up for questioning and held for
OL,15,Fnearly two weeks.
OL,17,FThe slander conviction carried a three-
OL,18,Fyear sentence, which Knox served
OL,19,Fduring nearly four years of detention
OL,20,Funtil a Perugia appeals court found
OL,21,Fher and Sollecito not guilty.
