OL,3,CItaly opens new slander trial against
OL,4,CAmanda Knox
OL,6,FAfter six years of flip-flop verdicts,
OL,7,FKnox was definitively exonerated by
OL,8,FItaly's highest court of the murder in
OL,9,F2015.
OL,11,FKercher's body was found with the
OL,12,Fthroat slit on November 2, 2007, in
OL,13,Fher locked bedroom in an apartment she
OL,14,Fshared with Knox and two other
OL,15,Froommates.
OL,17,F, whose DNA and footprints were found
OL,18,Fat the scene, was convicted of the
OL,19,Fmurder and sentenced to 16 years in
OL,20,Fprison. He was released after serving
OL,21,F13 years.
